{
  "texts": [
    "According to the results of this comparison, shown in Figure 5, it can be concluded that the models sharing only the embedding layer with CWS generally perform best on all datasets, which proves the effectiveness of the sharing mechanism proposed in this paper.",
    "Moreover, we can observe from the results that the models sharing both layers perform worse than the models sharing only the embedding layer and even worse than the non-joint models in most cases.",
    "This observation demonstrates that fully sharing the underlying mechanisms of CNER and CWS negatively affects the performance of the CNER task.",
    "Effects of the BCNN model.",
    "The proposed method BCNN-CWS mainly includes the joint training mechanism with CWS and the BCNN model."
  ]
}